    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runaround or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune, and priced to leave room for a bit of TLC. If you\u2019re after something straightforward, usable, and easy on the wallet, this could be a great fit.",
