      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with the right bones: engine fires up and the drivetrain feels complete, making this a great candidate for a budget build, parts car, or weekend revival. Cosmetic wear and age are present throughout, but the chassis has usable potential and the car still carries that planted, mechanical feel enthusiasts look for. A smart buy for someone who knows their way around a toolbox and wants an affordable platform with real upside.",
      "price": 6950.0,
