      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough, this car has the kind of honest character you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s the sort of ride that still turns an ordinary errand into a little adventure, with a well-worn charm that suggests plenty of stories already lived\u2014and plenty more waiting to be made. Perfect for a hands-on buyer, a budget-minded driver, or someone looking for a project with personality, this is an opportunity to own a car with soul at a price that leaves room for your vision.",
